@startuml
' V4 — Secret rotation lifecycle (write-ahead protocol, ADR-0006).
' Replica sub-lifecycle (T1 only): in-sync -> stale on rotation commit;
' stale -> in-sync on adapter push (events feed notification).
!include style.iuml

[*] --> Active
Active --> PendingStaged : batch planned;\nnew secret persisted (write-ahead)
PendingStaged --> Applied : connector set on target
PendingStaged --> Active : abort before apply;\ndiscard pending
Applied --> Verified : authenticated with new secret
Applied --> RollbackAttempt : verify failed
RollbackAttempt --> Active : old secret restored\nor still valid
RollbackAttempt --> Conflicted : manual intervention;\nboth secrets uncertain
Verified --> Active : new secret active;\nold retained
Active --> Retired : old secret revoked\nafter grace period

note right of PendingStaged
  lockout-safe: vault holds
  both values until verified
end note
note right of Conflicted
  alarm event —
  the kraken wakes
end note
@enduml
